
Name: Chicken a la King

Ingredients:

2 oz can sliced mushrooms
.25C chopped bell pepper
.25C butter
.25C lfour
1t salt
.125t pepper
1C chicken broth
1C cream
1C diced cooked chicken
.25C chipped pimiento

Instructions

Saute mushroom + bell pepper in butter
blend in flour, salt, pepper; let bubble
slowly stir in chicken broth + cream
bring to a boil over low heat, stirring constantly
boil one minute
add chicken + pimiento, het. 
serve over tost, waffle, biscuit, pastry shells, rice, etc.